ould well mean dead enchanters.  Dead enchanters often mean dead groups.  It's an ugly thing. <br>   Due to the gear limitations on monks, at high lvl's you will often see Warriors with Ac that is equal to, if not greater than that of a monk.  As to weapon restrictions, well lets just say that monks only have to worry about keeping three skills up to par, and our blunts are the best weapons in the game.  second to our fists once you get the epic of course.   </p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
